    dc:title "Review of the genus Typhloiulus Latzel, 1884 in the Dinaric region, with a description of four new species and the first description of the male of Typhloiulus insularis Strasser, 1938 (Diplopoda: Julida: Julidae)" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1457195>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1457197>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1457199>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1457209> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1457195>
    dc:description "FIGURE 13. Typhloiulus opisthonodus sp. nov., holotype male (NHMSC). A. Habitus, lateral view. B. Anterior part of the body, lateral view. C. Parts of the body rings 6 and 7, lateral view. D. Midbody rings, lateral view. E. Telson, lateral view. Arrow indicates ventral margin of body ring 7. Scale lines: 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1457195/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1457197>
    dc:description "FIGURE 14. Typhloiulus opisthonodus sp. nov., holotype male (NHMSC). A. First pair of legs, anterior view. B. Penis, posterior view. C. Promere, posterior view. D. Gonopods, mesal view. E. Mesomere and opisthomere, lateral view. F. Gonopods, lateral view. Abbreviations: l: lamella; m: mesomere; n: opisthomeral node; o: opisthomere; p: promere; s: solenomere; t: telopodite; v: velum; ml: mesal lobe. Scale line: 0.3 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1457197/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1457199>
    dc:description "FIGURE 15. Gonopods of representatives of the subgenus Inversotyphlus Strasser, 1962, mesal view. A. Typhloiulus clavatus sp. nov., holotype male (NHMSC). B. Typhloiulus gracilis sp. nov., paratype male (IZB). C. Typhloiulus opisthonodus sp. nov., holotype male (NHMSC). D. Typhloiulus lobifer Attems, 1951, male from Bitumen mine Minjera, island of Brač. E. Typhloiulus gellianae Makarov & Rađa, 2006, holotype male (ZDR). Scale lines: 0.1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1457199/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1457209>
    dc:description "FIGURE 20. Distribution of representatives of Inversotyphlus Strasser, 1962 and Typhloiulus edentulus Attems, 1951 (Attemsotyphlus Strasser, 1962)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1457209/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

